DE_LEIKA by Cleiton Palandrani (released May 2012)

Well, I worked on this map for three months... My idea was to make a map, with pleasant weather, with good lighting and easy gameplay.

I used custom sounds in some places, (wind chimes, classical music) you can check in CT spawn, bombsite A, long hall and other places... Were used custom sprites (flowers on the displacement) to make the environment more beautiful...

The map was well optimized, provides high fps and smooth gameplay.

- Can I play versus Bots?
- Yes! nav. built manually with place names for better gameplay!

Map details: 40 spawn points (20 vs 20), soundscapes, 3D skybox, radar overview, custom textures and models, custom sprites (vbsp), custom sounds.

Map design: Cleiton Palandrani

Important: All the custom content (except the nav) are embedded in the bsp.

Contributors/Credits: Thomas 'Hessi' Hess (www.thomashess.net) - some textures and models; Soenke 'Warby' Seidel (www.warby.de) - some textures and prop window; d00ds (http://d00ds.com) - light model, fish model.

Thanks: Thomas 'Hessi' Hess for allowing me to use their content.

Hope you give feedback; really love to listen to other peoples point of view for this map. Also can you please contact me if you're going to add to a server! My name is Mr Muffinz(on steam) Enjoy! Oh and there's more images inside the folder!:)

{La0aL} Grimlap & {La0aL} Trench Coat Warrior one are
proud to present de_Leetwood. de_Leetwood is a bomb 
defuse map designed with game play in mind. It was 
designed from the ground up to have everything we were 
looking for in a counterstrike map. Designed to look 
great, and play better. de_Leetwood takes place in 
the western town of Leetwood. Leetwood is settled in 
the Rocky Mountains, and proudly boasts the highest 
church in the county of leetsauce.

____________________________________________________

Terrorists' mission: Destroy Leetwood, using one of
the two target bomb sites.

Counter-Terrorists' mission: Stop the terrorists from
wiping Leetwood off the map.

____________________________________________________

Remember, wood cant stop a bullet in real life. 
And some walls are week enough to break through.

_____________________________________________________

Lake (de_lake) is a map for the Demolition, Arms Race, Flying Scoutsman, and Wingman modes featured in Counter-Strike: Global Offensive

Overview

Lake is a demolition map taking place at a small estate bordering a lake. The Terrorist faction for this map is the Phoenix Connexion and the Counter-Terroristfaction is SEAL Team 6.

Official Description (Demolition)

Counter-Terrorists: Prevent Terrorists from bombing the safe. Team members must defuse any bombs that threaten targeted area

.Terrorists: The Terrorist carrying the C4 must destroy the safe.

Trivia

  • As with most Demolition maps, this map is loosely based on a map from another Valve series, Left 4 Dead. It shares the basic layout with the last map (the Boathouse Finale) of the campaign Death Toll.

this is a bobm defuse map where the terrorist have to go trough a maze to find the bombzone. there are three weapons hidden whitin the map, the firstone is inside the wierd looking block, and the too others is further in to the wrong direction, both hidden inside blocks. while the terrorists is runing trough the maze, the counter terrorists have to chose betwen three different ways. the first one leads to a room containing AWP and a teleporter leading to the top of the map (the metalthing you can se one the overwievs. the second leads to a room with shotguns and then to the middle of the maze. the third leads to a M4 room and then to under the entire map, where they can kill the T from below. The CT can go to a secret room with buyzone as well. when the T have completed the maze, they push a button and goes into a room with the bombzone (watch the water, or else you COULD get killed, because there is where you come from after visiting the buyzone) plant the bomb quickly amd push the button under the arrow. a huge block will come up and block the path for the CT (exept for a space big as a door) making it easyer to suvive for the T´s.
If you need help finding secret areas, send a PM.
